plmxml_bus:QueryClause.stringValue: SELECT qid FROM ResourceAssignment WHERE "ResourcePool:secondary_object.group.name" = "${name = GROUP_NAME}" AND "ResourcePool:secondary_object.role.role_name" = "${role_name = ROLE_NAME}" AND "ResourcePool:secondary_object.all_members" = "${all_members = false}" AND "ScheduleTask:primary_object.fnd0state" = "${fnd0state = not_started}" AND "ScheduleTask:primary_object.schedule_tag.is_template" = "${is_template = false}" AND "ScheduleTask:primary_object.schedule_tag.published" = "${published = true}"

plmxml_bus:SavedQueryDef.name: __WorklistRPWFTask
plmxml_bus:SavedQueryDef.Description: Query to get non WF tasks assigned to RP

plmxml_bus:QueryClause.stringValue: SELECT qid FROM ResourceAssignment WHERE "ScheduleTask:primary_object.start_date" < "${start_date = TODAY+7}" AND "ScheduleTask:primary_object.workflow_template" IS_NULL "IS_NULL" AND "fnd0IsPlaceholder" = "${fnd0IsPlaceholder = false}"
